it gave me results, here it is shown in figure Figure 1


Code
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import numpy as np
import pandas

df = pandas.read_csv('data.csv')

def exponant(a):
    return 2**a

x = np.arange(0, 20, 1)
y = exponant(x)

plt.figure(1)
plt.title('graph of things')
plt.plot(x, y)
plt.show()
